Package com.cloudera.director.spi.v1.provider

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CloudProvider
    A cloud provider, which may support multiple cloud resource types.
    CloudProviderMetadata
    Provides metadata about a cloud provider.
    CredentialsProvider<T>
    Represents a provider of cloud credentials.
    CredentialsProviderMetadata
    Metadata about a credentials provider.
    InstanceProvider<I extends Instance<T>,T extends InstanceTemplate>
    Represents a provider of instances.
    Launcher
    Cloud provider plugin launcher.
    ProviderMetadata
    Metadata about a provider.
    ResourceProvider<R extends Resource<T>,T extends ResourceTemplate>
    Represents a provider of cloud resources.
    ResourceProviderMetadata
    Provider metadata about a resource provider.
